hopobject.body: My battery's about to run out elibriumconsulting.com Comp store sales in the Americas were equal to last year and in line with our expectation. Performance varied geographically, with growth in the New York flagship store sale, tied to both increased local and tourist demand, being offset by a slight decline in comparable brand store sales. And those brand store results were mixed by market, with no discernible pattern except for pronounced softness in Hawaii and Guam, reflecting a decline in Japanese tourist sales that we believe is attributed to the weaker yen.
